data.description: Welcome home! This charming property is nestled in the heart of Plainfield's Westmere subdivision. With 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and a large loft, this home offers a cozy and practical space. 2 of the bedrooms have walk-in closets! On the main floor, the living area and study/rec space have updated floors, radiating a fresh and inviting ambiance. Adorned with an updated kitchen backsplash, meal preparation will be a breeze in this stylish and functional space. Additional improvements include new toilets in 2022 and a new water heater in 2019. Outside, there is a great backyard to enjoy. Located close to shopping and restaurants, this home is the perfect place to create lasting memories.
